NAME

    OpenTracing::Integration::DBI - support DBI tracing

SYNOPSIS

     use OpenTracing::Integration qw(DBI);
     my $dbh = DBI->connect(...);
     $dbh->selectall_arrayref(qw{select * from information_schema.tables});

DESCRIPTION

    See OpenTracing::Integration for more details.

